page.title: 20SHERE, SURREY. JULY 1985
page.content: This section of the Domesday Project has been compiled by 21 children, aged 7 and 8 years, pupils at Shere C.of E. First School. Please bear in mind the work has been completed by this age group. We have enjoyed taking part in this venture and hope you enjoy reading about a small village in Surrey. Joanne Lee 8 Ann Livingston 8 Shulay Steere 8 Ben Howard 8 Matthew Cox 8 Coralie Field 8 Kirsty Davey 7 Anthony Weller 7 Jake Hughes 8 Sarah Druce 8 Lucy Barker 8 Chris Savage 7 Philip Stuart 7 Emma Chapman 7 Jeremy Osborn 7 Pauline Strudwick 7 Ben Walton 7 Makayla Herd 6 Claire Tyrrell7 James Daniels 7 Kelly Smith 7 Mrs. M.
